RHEL中mail的使用
1、SendMail
	$>mail -s "title" usrname
	text
	.<退出编译>
	Cc:

	$>mail -s "title" usrname < text.mail


2、RecvMail

	$>mail
	"/var/spool/mail/root": 1 message 1 unread
	>N 1 xxxxxxxx@localho ......
	&1
	q "quit and move to ~/mbox"
	x "quit"

